that measures are put in place that will force these super markets to get
their produce from our own institution," she said.
</P>
<P>
The Zambia National Farmers Union recently called on the government to
impose eye-for-eye non-tariff barriers on all horticultural produce from
neighboring South Africa and Zimbabwe , enabling Zambian farmers to compete
fairly. 
