from the New Year holiday. Most of the people who lost their homes sought
refuge in the nearby churches and neighbors' homes.
</P>
<P>
The fire is suspected to have been caused by a stove that exploded in a
nine-room house.
</P>
<P>
Witnesses said a tenant had lit a stove to prepare a meal but went out to
drink palm wine, apparently forgetting the stove.
</P>
<P>
Mombasa police said they are still trying to establish the cause of the
fire. 
